Hi all,

two Master students supervised by myself and Julian Togelius made a program
where people can build brains in a game-like context. The goal of this
project is to find out how good people are at building these complex
networks and if they can do it better collaboratively. If you could play
the "game" and spread the word that would be great!

Looking forward to your comments.

You can find it here: http://braincrafter.dk/

Cheers,
Sebastian
